commit.message: Harfbuzz can do kerning positioning even if the font hasn't the data (see #341)
Sync SDL3_ttf wiki -> header

Updated for the SDL3 RW -> IO changes

Fixes https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL_ttf/issues/344
Corrected CMake image/ttf mixups
Pass kerning setting through into harfbuzz shaping
Updated for recent SDL3 changes
SDL's memcpy now turns into optimized assembly where possible
Add spaces around SDL_PRI??? to avoid potential compiler warnings.
upgrade vendored freetype to 2.13.2 with fixes
Add TTF_SetFontLanguage to set language BCP47 code, (see #308)

Don't fail if passed multiple newlines as text

Fixes https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL_ttf/issues/311

(cherry picked from commit 2089f482c81decf402cc0fe6c2887195ed9dff43)

Added a -wrap option to showfont

(cherry picked from commit e65b1e37cd16f155ccf89dba728d01e0fd554c42)
Sync SDL3_ttf wiki -> header

Updated documentation to reflect when the font source is closed

Fixes https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL_ttf/issues/317

(cherry picked from commit f829625cf157f0fdc0e9687b03e1dfd8abae74a5)
cmake: build static library by default for platforms that don't support shared libraries
Removed camel case from xcframework target in Xcode
Fix ASAN reports: runtime error: left shift of XXX by 24 places cannot be represented in type 'int'

Fixed bug #324 - prevent unaligned load access
use memcpy so we can expect the compiler to optimize when possible

Prevent negative draw line and out of bounds.

can be reproduced with testapp.c, int seed = 1704796537, at iteration ~270
update vendored harfbuzz

xcode: fix the list of files from the harfbuzz library.

The Xcode project was referring to some files that don't exist in the
Harfbuzz project anymore, this commit also added some .cc files that were
missing to build the library using Xcode.
Updated copyright for 2024
.gitmodules: fix harfbuzz branch name.
Updated VisualC project to match harfbuzz sources.
Add Get-Gitmodules.ps1
cmake: SDL_detect_linker needs set(PARENT_SCOPE)
cmake: detect linker id, and assume MSVC does not support version scripts
fix build after SDL_WaitEvent return type change in SDL3
cmake: fix MSVC unrecognized option link warning
Remove deprecated SDL_TTF_COMPILEDVERSION
